com.enremmeta.rtb.api

Class UserFrequencyCapAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enremmeta.rtb.api.UserFrequencyCapAttributes

  • public class UserFrequencyCapAttributes
extends Object
    Bid and Impression histories for Frequency Cap calculations. In getCount functions the history older than FC time frame is being cleaned. In updateImpression functions the history of Bids earlier the impression is being cleaned.
    Author:
    Vladimir Zamyatin (boba@opendsp.com)

    Copyright Â© Enremmeta LLC 2015. All Rights Reserved.
